cc:Work.dc:title: Box - HalfBox
cc:Work.dc:description:
Configurable half of a box which can be: a bookend, a hanging shelf, an angle clamping jig, ...
This can be used to create:
* a hanging shelf: ![HalfBox as hanging shelf](static/samples/HalfBox_Shelf_usage.jpg)
* an angle clamping jig: ![HalfBox as an angle clamping jig](static/samples/HalfBox_AngleJig_usage.jpg)
* a bookend: ![HalfBox as a bookend](static/samples/HalfBox_Bookend_usage.jpg)
and many more...
Created with Boxes.py (https://boxes.hackerspace-bamberg.de/) Command line: boxes HalfBox Command line short: boxes HalfBox
